00:17:19.890 --> 00:17:21.859 align:middle line:84%
But there's a curious
thing about biochemistry.

00:17:21.859 --> 00:17:23.440 align:middle line:84%
You're doing
biochemistry, to study

00:17:23.440 --> 00:17:25.319 align:middle line:90%
the molecular basis of life.

00:17:25.319 --> 00:17:27.360 align:middle line:84%
