you do in the laboratory

00:17:27.360 --> 00:17:29.650 align:middle line:84%
is kill whatever
you're studying.

00:17:29.650 --> 00:17:32.590 align:middle line:84%
Grind it up, extract
the enzymes, and then,

00:17:32.590 --> 00:17:34.670 align:middle line:84%
in a test tube,
study the properties

00:17:34.670 --> 00:17:36.590 align:middle line:84%
of some of these
molecules extracted

00:17:36.590 --> 00:17:38.740 align:middle line:90%
from this killed organism.

00:17:38.740 --> 00:17:42.350 align:middle line:84%
