00:17:49.120 --> 00:17:52.700 align:middle line:84%
else thought it definitely was
the best way to study life,

00:17:52.700 --> 00:17:57.150 align:middle line:84%
and in fact, there was
no other valid way.

00:17:57.150 --> 00:17:59.930 align:middle line:90%
So this set me thinking.

00:17:59.930 --> 00:18:03.430 align:middle line:84%
