the science of biology

00:18:03.430 --> 00:18:07.160 align:middle line:84%
could be reformed, that this
idea that living organisms

00:18:07.160 --> 00:18:09.940 align:middle line:84%
are truly life, rather
than being just machines,

00:18:09.940 --> 00:18:12.760 align:middle line:84%
whereas the official doctrine
in mechanistic theory

00:18:12.760 --> 00:18:17.170 align:middle line:84%
says living organisms are
just complicated machines.

00:18:17.170 --> 00:18:19.670 align:middle line:84%
Believe it or not, it's
still the official doctrine

00:18:19.670 --> 00:18:24.060 align:middle line:84%
of academic biology
and academic medicine.

00:18:24.060 --> 00:18:27.720 align:middle line:90%
These ideas went on developing.

00:18:27.720 --> 00:18:30.490 align:middle line:84%
I then saw how I could
bring them all together

00:18:30.490 --> 00:18:34.100 align:middle line:84%
in a synthesis, and
