00:23:17.320 --> 00:23:20.780 align:middle line:84%
to theories in science,
to new works of art,

00:23:20.780 --> 00:23:25.410 align:middle line:84%
to new forms of culture, to
instincts in birds and animals,

00:23:25.410 --> 00:23:27.910 align:middle line:84%
to the forms of flowers,
and plants, and leaves,

00:23:27.910 --> 00:23:30.250 align:middle line:84%
to the many kinds of
rocks and crystals,

00:23:30.250 --> 00:23:32.570 align:middle line:84%
and to all the forms of
galactic, and stellar,

00:23:32.570 --> 00:23:34.830 align:middle line:90%
and planetary organization?

