00:27:42.040 --> 00:27:45.840 align:middle line:84%
the appetition of human
history for greater

00:27:45.840 --> 00:27:49.160 align:middle line:90%
expression of complexity.

00:27:49.160 --> 00:27:55.960 align:middle line:84%
So when I think about these
terms-- chaos, creativity,

00:27:55.960 --> 00:28:00.270 align:middle line:84%
imagination-- I see
them as a three stroke

00:28:00.270 --> 00:28:02.750 align:middle line:90%
engine of some sort.

00:28:02.750 --> 00:28:11.110 align:middle line:84%
Each impels and runs the other,
and sets up a reinforcing cycle

00:28:11.110 --> 00:28:16.030 align:middle line:84%
