organisms, processes,

00:28:16.030 --> 00:28:20.380 align:middle line:84%
that are caught up in this
in the phenomenon of being.

00:28:20.380 --> 00:28:27.220 align:middle line:84%
The phenomenon of being is
this self-synergizing engine

00:28:27.220 --> 00:28:30.570 align:middle line:84%
out of chaos,
through creativity,

00:28:30.570 --> 00:28:34.840 align:middle line:84%
into the imagination,
back into chaos, out

00:28:34.840 --> 00:28:38.520 align:middle line:84%
into creativity, and
so forth, and so on.

00:28:38.520 --> 00:28:42.860 align:middle line:84%
And it operates on many
levels simultaneously,

00:28:42.860 --> 00:28:48.650 align:middle line:84%
so that the planet is
undergoing a destiny.

00:28:48.650 --> 00:28:53.130 align:middle line:84%
Deep time, the time of geology,
was only really discovered

00:28:53.130 --> 00:28:55.530 align:middle line:90%
around the turn of the century.

00:28:55.530 --> 00:29:02.820 align:middle line:84%
And it is cosmically ennobling
to think of the universe

00:29:02.820 --> 00:29:05.190 align:middle line:90%
as a thing of great age.

00:29:05.190 --> 00:29:10.180 align:middle line:84%
But I think that it's
time to put in place, next

00:29:10.180 --> 00:29:14.300 align:middle line:84%
to the notion of deep
cosmic time, the notion

00:29:14.300 --> 00:29:24.000 align:middle line:84%
of chaotic, sudden change, cusp
flux, and sudden perturbation.

00:29:24.000 --> 00:29:27.870 align:middle line:84%
Because what deep
time has revealed,

00:29:27.870 --> 00:29:30.870 align:middle line:84%
as we've pushed our
understanding of the career

00:29:30.870 --> 00:29:35.000 align:middle line:84%
of organic life back
65 million years,

00:29:35.000 --> 00:29:41.750 align:middle line:84%
270 million years, what we
see is tremendous punctuation

00:29:41.750 --> 00:29:43.270 align:middle line:90%
built into the universe.

00:29:43.270 --> 00:29:47.410 align:middle line:84%
