the form of asteroidal impacts,

00:29:47.410 --> 00:29:51.240 align:middle line:84%
this thing which happened
65 million years ago,

00:29:51.240 --> 00:29:55.220 align:middle line:84%
nothing larger than a
chicken walked away from it

00:29:55.220 --> 00:29:57.200 align:middle line:90%
on this planet.

00:29:57.200 --> 00:30:00.860 align:middle line:84%
So there's a strange
paradox, where

00:30:00.860 --> 00:30:05.830 align:middle line:84%
taking deep time seriously,
the message of deep time is you

00:30:05.830 --> 00:30:09.480 align:middle line:84%
may not have as much
time as you thought,

00:30:09.480 --> 00:30:14.040 align:middle line:84%
that the universe is
dynamic, capable of turning

00:30:14.040 --> 00:30:15.790 align:middle line:90%
sudden corners.

00:30:15.790 --> 00:30:20.980 align:middle line:84%
So then the imagination
becomes a beacon.

00:30:20.980 --> 00:30:27.530 align:middle line:84%
The imagination is, as it
were, a scout sent ahead,

00:30:27.530 --> 00:30:34.860 align:middle line:84%
or something which has preceded
us into history, and in fact,

00:30:34.860 --> 00:30:38.110 align:middle line:84%
is a kind of
eschatological object.

00:30:38.110 --> 00:30:43.570 align:middle line:84%
It is shedding influence,
the morpho-genetic field,

00:30:43.570 --> 00:30:44.230 align:middle line:90%
if you wish.

00:30:44.230 --> 00:30:47.370 align:middle line:84%
If the morpho-genetic
field is not

00:30:47.370 --> 00:30:51.260 align:middle line:84%
subject to the inverse square
law of decreased influence

00:30:51.260 --> 00:30:57.120 align:middle line:84%
over distance, then I, as
a layman, don't see why,

00:30:57.120 --> 00:31:03.880 align:middle line:84%
Rupert, we couldn't locate it
at the conclusion of process.

00:31:03.880 --> 00:31:07.250 align:middle line:84%
Because one of the things that's
always puzzled me about the Big

00:31:07.250 --> 00:31:12.890 align:middle line:90%
Bang is it's a singularity.

00:31:12.890 --> 00:31:15.570 align:middle line:84%
This is the term
physicists use for it.

00:31:15.570 --> 00:31:19.330 align:middle line:84%
This means theory
cannot predict it,

00:31:19.330 --> 00:31:23.900 align:middle line:84%
and yet it is necessary to make
everything which follows from

00:31:23.900 --> 00:31:25.350 align:middle line:90%
it happen.

00:31:25.350 --> 00:31:28.050 align:middle line:84%
So you just say there's
no reason for this.

00:31:28.050 --> 00:31:31.100 align:middle line:84%
We have no argument for this,
but the rest of the theory

00:31:31.100 --> 00:31:32.130 align:middle line:90%
needs it.

00:31:32.130 --> 00:31:37.020 align:middle line:84%
So it's a singularity, and
the immense improbability,

00:31:37.020 --> 00:31:42.130 align:middle line:84%
which modern science rests
on, but cares not to discuss,

00:31:42.130 --> 00:31:47.300 align:middle line:84%
is this-- the belief that the
universe sprang from nothing

00:31:47.300 --> 00:31:49.590 align:middle line:90%
in a single moment.

00:31:49.590 --> 00:31:54.140 align:middle line:84%
Well, if you can make that
leap, to believe that,

00:31:54.140 --> 00:31:57.050 align:middle line:84%
it's very hard to see
what you couldn't believe.

00:31:57.050 --> 00:32:03.670 align:middle line:84%
That is almost the limiting case
of credulity, I would think.

00:32:03.670 --> 00:32:15.070 align:middle line:90%


00:32:15.070 --> 00:32:17.490 align:middle line:84%
So in order to save
the phenomenon,

00:32:17.490 --> 00:32:21.780 align:middle line:84%
I would propose
a different idea.

00:32:21.780 --> 00:32:24.850 align:middle line:84%
And I think it is
eminently reasonable.

00:32:24.850 --> 00:32:31.110 align:middle line:84%
And it is that as the complexity
of a system increases,

00:32:31.110 --> 00:32:37.640 align:middle line:84%
so too does the likelihood of
its generating a singularity,

00:32:37.640 --> 00:32:40.840 align:middle line:84%
or an unpredictable
perturbation.

00:32:40.840 --> 00:32:45.290 align:middle line:84%
So the pre-existent
state of the universe

00:32:45.290 --> 00:32:50.270 align:middle line:84%
I imagine to be extremely
simple, and unflawed

00:32:50.270 --> 00:32:55.330 align:middle line:84%
nothingness, in other words,
the least likely situation

00:32:55.330 --> 00:32:58.790 align:middle line:84%
in which you would expect
a singularity to emerge.

00:32:58.790 --> 00:33:02.940 align:middle line:84%
But now let's look at the other
end of the historical continuum

00:33:02.940 --> 00:33:05.750 align:middle line:90%
of the history of the universe.

00:33:05.750 --> 00:33:09.300 align:middle line:84%
Let's look at the
world we're living,

00:33:09.300 --> 00:33:17.050 align:middle line:84%
which is full of 106 elements,
tremendous gradients of energy,

00:33:17.050 --> 00:33:22.400 align:middle line:84%
ranging from what's going on
inside pulsars and quasars,

00:33:22.400 --> 00:33:26.680 align:middle line:84%
to what is going on
inside viruses and cells,

00:33:26.680 --> 00:33:32.060 align:middle line:84%
tremendous organizational
capacity at the atomic level,

00:33:32.060 --> 00:33:35.160 align:middle line:84%
at the molecular
level, at the level

00:33:35.160 --> 00:33:38.860 align:middle line:84%
of molecular
polymerization, at the level

00:33:38.860 --> 00:33:42.330 align:middle line:84%
of membranes and
gels, at the level

00:33:42.330 --> 00:33:47.715 align:middle line:84%
of cells and organelles,
organisms, societies,

00:33:47.715 --> 00:33:49.150 align:middle line:90%
and so forth, and so on.

00:33:49.150 --> 00:33:52.720 align:middle line:84%
In other words, the
universe, at this moment,

00:33:52.720 --> 00:33:57.930 align:middle line:84%
is a tremendously complicated,
integrated, multi-leveled,

00:33:57.930 --> 00:33:59.520 align:middle line:90%
dynamic thing.

00:33:59.520 --> 00:34:04.120 align:middle line:84%
And every passing moment,
it becomes more so.

00:34:04.120 --> 00:34:07.870 align:middle line:84%
This is what evolution,
history, compression

00:34:07.870 --> 00:34:09.320 align:middle line:84%
of time-- what all
of these things

00:34:09.320 --> 00:34:11.870 align:middle line:84%
are attempting to
indicate is the increasing

00:34:11.870 --> 00:34:13.749 align:middle line:90%
complexity of reality.

00:34:13.749 --> 00:34:18.960 align:middle line:90%


00:34:18.960 --> 00:34:23.780 align:middle line:84%
If a singularity is necessary
to explain this universe,

00:34:23.780 --> 00:34:26.360 align:middle line:84%
that singularity
must emerge rather

00:34:26.360 --> 00:34:30.860 align:middle line:84%
near the end of the
complexification process

00:34:30.860 --> 00:34:33.380 align:middle line:90%
rather than its beginning.

00:34:33.380 --> 00:34:37.449 align:middle line:84%
You see, we simply have to
reverse our preconceptions

00:34:37.449 --> 00:34:40.530 align:middle line:84%
about the flow of
cause and effect,

00:34:40.530 --> 00:34:44.250 align:middle line:84%
and then we get
a great attractor

00:34:44.250 --> 00:34:49.469 align:middle line:84%
that pulls all organization
and structure toward itself

00:34:49.469 --> 00:34:51.449 align:middle line:90%
over several billion years.

00:34:51.449 --> 00:34:56.969 align:middle line:84%
And as the objects
of its attraction

00:34:56.969 --> 00:35:02.550 align:middle line:84%
grow closer to its proximity,
they somehow interpenetrate.

00:35:02.550 --> 00:35:07.002 align:middle line:84%
They set up standing wave
patterns of interference.

00:35:07.002 --> 00:35:09.980 align:middle line:90%


00:35:09.980 --> 00:35:14.220 align:middle line:84%
New properties become
emergent, and the entire thing

00:35:14.220 --> 00:35:15.820 align:middle line:90%
complexifies.

00:35:15.820 --> 00:35:23.160 align:middle line:84%
Well, to my mind, this is
the divine imagination.

00:35:23.160 --> 00:35:25.945 align:middle line:90%
This is what Blake called it.

00:35:25.945 --> 00:35:29.290 align:middle line:84%
This is the only way
I can conceive of it.

00:35:29.290 --> 00:35:33.790 align:middle line:84%
Time is the theater
of God's becoming.

00:35:33.790 --> 00:35:36.180 align:middle line:84%
But it's also, from
the point of view

00:35:36.180 --> 00:35:38.580 align:middle line:84%
of a higher
dimensional manifold,

00:35:38.580 --> 00:35:41.380 align:middle line:90%
a kind of fait accompli.

00:35:41.380 --> 00:35:43.170 align:middle line:90%
And this is no contradiction.

00:35:43.170 --> 00:35:44.720 align:middle line:90%
Or if it is, it's all right.

00:35:44.720 --> 00:35:47.570 align:middle line:84%
Because in these realms
of higher ontology,

00:35:47.570 --> 00:35:52.300 align:middle line:84%
you're always asked to
avoid closure, and hold

00:35:52.300 --> 00:35:55.580 align:middle line:84%
the notion of a
coincidentia oppositorum,

00:35:55.580 --> 00:35:57.400 align:middle line:90%
a union of opposites.

00:35:57.400 --> 00:36:02.060 align:middle line:84%
The thing is both what it
is, and what it is not,

00:36:02.060 --> 00:36:05.120 align:middle line:84%
and yet it somehow
escapes contradiction.

00:36:05.120 --> 00:36:09.860 align:middle line:84%
And that's how the open
system is maintained.

00:36:09.860 --> 00:36:16.280 align:middle line:84%
That's how the miracle
of life is possible.

00:36:16.280 --> 00:36:19.850 align:middle line:84%
So I think of the
divine imagination

00:36:19.850 --> 00:36:28.390 align:middle line:84%
as the class of all things
both possible and beautiful.

00:36:28.390 --> 00:36:31.280 align:middle line:84%
It's a kind of
reverse Platonism.

00:36:31.280 --> 00:36:36.200 align:middle line:84%
The attractor is at the bottom
of a very deep pit into which

00:36:36.200 --> 00:36:40.690 align:middle line:90%
all phenomena is cascading.

00:36:40.690 --> 00:36:44.100 align:middle line:84%
What is taught in
modern universities

00:36:44.100 --> 00:36:48.980 align:middle line:84%
these days is that these tracks
in the snow are going nowhere.

00:36:48.980 --> 00:36:53.790 align:middle line:84%
The technical term is
"trendlessly fluctuating."

00:36:53.790 --> 00:36:57.560 align:middle line:84%
And we're told that history
is this kind of process.

00:36:57.560 --> 00:37:00.290 align:middle line:90%
It's trendlessly fluctuating.

00:37:00.290 --> 00:37:01.420 align:middle line:90%
It goes here.

00:37:01.420 --> 00:37:02.540 align:middle line:90%
It goes there.

00:37:02.540 --> 00:37:06.495 align:middle line:84%
It's called a "random walk"
in information theory.

00:37:06.495 --> 00:37:09.230 align:middle line:90%
It means you just wander around.

00:37:09.230 --> 00:37:11.390 align:middle line:90%
And well, it's very interesting.

00:37:11.390 --> 00:37:17.790 align:middle line:84%
Now we begin to see through the
marvel of the new mathematics

00:37:17.790 --> 00:37:22.650 align:middle line:84%
that random walks are not random
at all, that a sufficiently

00:37:22.650 --> 00:37:26.566 align:middle line:84%
long random walk becomes
a fractal structure

00:37:26.566 --> 00:37:29.810 align:middle line:84%
of extraordinary
depth and beauty.

00:37:29.810 --> 00:37:33.530 align:middle line:84%
So you see, really
what has to happen

00:37:33.530 --> 00:37:38.000 align:middle line:84%
is for us to see
chaos not as something

00:37:38.000 --> 00:37:44.250 align:middle line:84%
that degrades information, and
is somehow the enemy of order,

00:37:44.250 --> 00:37:49.030 align:middle line:84%
but rather chaos is the
birthplace of order.

00:37:49.030 --> 00:37:51.060 align:middle line:90%
Chaos is not the problem.

00:37:51.060 --> 00:37:53.460 align:middle line:90%
Chaos is the answer.

