01:06:00.740 --> 01:06:03.450 align:middle line:90%
And I think that's a great idea.

01:06:03.450 --> 01:06:05.930 align:middle line:90%
Let's just make it true enough.

01:06:05.930 --> 01:06:10.650 align:middle line:10%
Because that's as true
as it can be gotten.

01:06:10.650 --> 01:06:16.810 align:middle line:90%
Well, the imagination is chaos.

01:06:16.810 --> 01:06:21.170 align:middle line:84%
New forms are fetched
out of this chaos.

01:06:21.170 --> 01:06:27.420 align:middle line:84%
For me, the creative act is
the letting down of the net

01:06:27.420 --> 01:06:32.700 align:middle line:84%
of human imagination into the
ocean of chaos on which we are

01:06:32.700 --> 01:06:38.450 align:middle line:84%
suspended, and the attempt
to bring out of it ideas,

01:06:38.450 --> 01:06:39.830 align:middle line:90%
to bring out of it-- sometimes--

01:06:39.830 --> 01:06:42.430 align:middle line:90%


01:06:42.430 --> 01:06:46.130 align:middle line:84%
This is my model for the
psychedelic experience,

01:06:46.130 --> 01:06:48.230 align:middle line:84%
that it is the
night sea journey,

01:06:48.230 --> 01:06:54.040 align:middle line:84%
that it is the lone fisherman
on a tropical sea with his nets.

01:06:54.040 --> 01:06:58.750 align:middle line:84%
And you let these nets
down, and sometimes,

01:06:58.750 --> 01:07:02.860 align:middle line:84%
something tears through them
that leaves them in shreds.

01:07:02.860 --> 01:07:06.990 align:middle line:84%
And you just row for shore, and
put your head under your bed,

01:07:06.990 --> 01:07:08.210 align:middle line:90%
and pray.

01:07:08.210 --> 01:07:11.080 align:middle line:84%
And at other times,
what slips through are

01:07:11.080 --> 01:07:16.160 align:middle line:84%
the minutiae, the minnows of
this ichthyological metaphor

01:07:16.160 --> 01:07:18.630 align:middle line:90%
of idea chasing.

01:07:18.630 --> 01:07:24.370 align:middle line:84%
But sometimes, you actually
can bring home something that

01:07:24.370 --> 01:07:29.450 align:middle line:84%
is food, that is food for
the human community, that we

01:07:29.450 --> 01:07:33.240 align:middle line:84%
can sustain ourselves
on, and go forward.

01:07:33.240 --> 01:07:37.960 align:middle line:84%
So we haven't talked that
much about art and aesthetics,

01:07:37.960 --> 01:07:46.580 align:middle line:84%
but I think, in the human
world, the appetition

01:07:46.580 --> 01:07:49.670 align:middle line:90%
is for beauty, to my mind.

01:07:49.670 --> 01:07:53.640 align:middle line:84%
And this is another place where
the Platonism shines radiantly

01:07:53.640 --> 01:07:54.540 align:middle line:90%
through.

01:07:54.540 --> 01:07:58.520 align:middle line:84%
Because Plato held that
the good was the true,

01:07:58.520 --> 01:08:01.880 align:middle line:84%
and that both were
the beautiful.

01:08:01.880 --> 01:08:05.540 align:middle line:84%
And this is a very quaint
idea from the point of view

01:08:05.540 --> 01:08:09.300 align:middle line:84%
of modern philosophy,
but I think

01:08:09.300 --> 01:08:14.730 align:middle line:84%
it's in the bones, when you
actually connect yourself up

01:08:14.730 --> 01:08:16.029 align:middle line:90%
to the planet.

01:08:16.029 --> 01:08:23.520 align:middle line:84%
That's why chaos is capable of
being the tremendous repository

01:08:23.520 --> 01:08:26.510 align:middle line:90%
ordered beauty that it is.

01:08:26.510 --> 01:08:33.609 align:middle line:84%
Because there is no chaos,
in the old definition, which

01:08:33.609 --> 01:08:38.130 align:middle line:84%
is to say that which by
any definition or any test

01:08:38.130 --> 01:08:40.410 align:middle line:90%
is found to be disordered.

01:08:40.410 --> 01:08:46.340 align:middle line:84%
That is just a kind
of hell notion,

01:08:46.340 --> 01:08:50.939 align:middle line:84%
a kind of hypostasization of
an ultimate state of disorder.

01:08:50.939 --> 01:08:57.180 align:middle line:84%
But nowhere in the world that is
deployed through space and time

01:08:57.180 --> 01:08:58.270 align:middle line:90%
do you encounter that.

01:08:58.270 --> 01:09:01.660 align:middle line:84%
Instead, what you
encounter is embedded order

01:09:01.660 --> 01:09:07.840 align:middle line:84%
upon embedded order,
this fractal thing.

01:09:07.840 --> 01:09:12.620 align:middle line:84%
And then finally, for
me, the imagination

01:09:12.620 --> 01:09:15.770 align:middle line:90%
is the goal of history.

01:09:15.770 --> 01:09:22.830 align:middle line:84%
I see culture as an effort
to literally realize

01:09:22.830 --> 01:09:25.160 align:middle line:90%
our collective dreams.

01:09:25.160 --> 01:09:30.060 align:middle line:84%
And it's on a very crude level,
when it's you make your mask,

01:09:30.060 --> 01:09:33.689 align:middle line:84%
and I make my mask, and then
we dance around together.

01:09:33.689 --> 01:09:35.970 align:middle line:84%
And it's even at a
very crude level, when

01:09:35.970 --> 01:09:38.710 align:middle line:84%
it's you design
your shopping mall,

01:09:38.710 --> 01:09:40.810 align:middle line:84%
and I'll design my
World Trade Center,

01:09:40.810 --> 01:09:43.790 align:middle line:84%
and we'll put them on the
same piece of real estate.

01:09:43.790 --> 01:09:47.600 align:middle line:84%
But we're coming
now through media,

01:09:47.600 --> 01:09:50.930 align:middle line:84%
I believe, through virtual
reality, and human machine

01:09:50.930 --> 01:09:53.630 align:middle line:84%
integration, and this
kind of the thing,

01:09:53.630 --> 01:09:57.690 align:middle line:84%
into a situation
where the imagination

01:09:57.690 --> 01:10:02.100 align:middle line:84%
is going to be something
that we can share,

01:10:02.100 --> 01:10:06.200 align:middle line:84%
that the path of mind
through its own meanderings

01:10:06.200 --> 01:10:10.050 align:middle line:84%
will become something that can
be recorded, and played back.

01:10:10.050 --> 01:10:13.780 align:middle line:84%
We will have the possibility
of living in our own past,

01:10:13.780 --> 01:10:20.710 align:middle line:84%
or creating and trading
realities as art.

01:10:20.710 --> 01:10:25.420 align:middle line:84%
And art as life lived
in the imagination

01:10:25.420 --> 01:10:29.260 align:middle line:84%
is the great archetype,
which rears itself up

01:10:29.260 --> 01:10:32.256 align:middle line:84%
at the end of history--
life in the imagination.

01:10:32.256 --> 01:10:38.620 align:middle line:84%
The imagination is
this auric field,

01:10:38.620 --> 01:10:41.970 align:middle line:84%
which surrounds the
transcendental object

01:10:41.970 --> 01:10:45.210 align:middle line:84%
at greater and greater
depth as you approach

01:10:45.210 --> 01:10:47.190 align:middle line:90%
the transcendental object.

01:10:47.190 --> 01:10:50.510 align:middle line:84%
And as we now close
distance with it,

01:10:50.510 --> 01:10:58.590 align:middle line:84%
all of our cultural expression,
all of our self-awareness

01:10:58.590 --> 01:11:02.395 align:middle line:84%
is taking on this
curiously designed quality.

01:11:02.395 --> 01:11:04.450 align:middle line:10%
I mean, you must
have noticed this,

01:11:04.450 --> 01:11:08.590 align:middle line:10%
that the world is very
heavily designed in a way

01:11:08.590 --> 01:11:11.410 align:middle line:10%
that it never was before.

01:11:11.410 --> 01:11:15.220 align:middle line:84%
Morpho-genetic fields
of great size and scope,

01:11:15.220 --> 01:11:19.210 align:middle line:84%
which are international schools
of architecture and design,

01:11:19.210 --> 01:11:21.140 align:middle line:90%
touch whole continents.

01:11:21.140 --> 01:11:25.790 align:middle line:84%
Entire cities are given
certain ambiences.

01:11:25.790 --> 01:11:28.990 align:middle line:84%
This is the summoning
of the imagination

01:11:28.990 --> 01:11:31.330 align:middle line:90%
into the human scale.

01:11:31.330 --> 01:11:37.510 align:middle line:84%
It's like a god that we wish to
call down, and draw to Earth.

01:11:37.510 --> 01:11:39.520 align:middle line:84%
I mean, this is why
William Blake called

01:11:39.520 --> 01:11:42.240 align:middle line:90%
it the divine imagination.

01:11:42.240 --> 01:11:45.370 align:middle line:84%
Because it is the
four-gated city.

01:11:45.370 --> 01:11:46.990 align:middle line:90%
It is the flying saucer.

01:11:46.990 --> 01:11:53.190 align:middle line:84%
We are on a journey to
meet this great attractor,

01:11:53.190 --> 01:11:55.190 align:middle line:84%
and as we close
distance with it,

01:11:55.190 --> 01:11:58.880 align:middle line:84%
it is more and more
a multifaceted mirror

01:11:58.880 --> 01:12:02.850 align:middle line:90%
of our images of beauty.

01:12:02.850 --> 01:12:04.760 align:middle line:84%
So it's like an
ascending learning

01:12:04.760 --> 01:12:07.500 align:middle line:90%
curve that becomes asymptotic.

01:12:07.500 --> 01:12:10.470 align:middle line:84%
And at that point,
you're face to face

01:12:10.470 --> 01:12:16.430 align:middle line:84%
with a mystery, a
living mystery that

01:12:16.430 --> 01:12:19.390 align:middle line:90%
is within each and all of us.

01:12:19.390 --> 01:12:25.340 align:middle line:84%
It's the imagination that
argues for the divine spark

01:12:25.340 --> 01:12:26.760 align:middle line:90%
in human beings.

01:12:26.760 --> 01:12:29.200 align:middle line:84%
It's absolutely
confounding, if you

01:12:29.200 --> 01:12:33.550 align:middle line:84%
try to get biology
to produce it for you

01:12:33.550 --> 01:12:35.480 align:middle line:90%
as a necessary quantity.

01:12:35.480 --> 01:12:36.720 align:middle line:90%
It isn't that.

01:12:36.720 --> 01:12:39.330 align:middle line:90%
It's an emanation from above.

01:12:39.330 --> 01:12:46.450 align:middle line:84%
It is literally a descent of
the world soul into all of us.

01:12:46.450 --> 01:12:51.100 align:middle line:84%
We then become the
atoms of the world soul,

01:12:51.100 --> 01:12:55.380 align:middle line:84%
and our channel to it
is by closing our eyes,

01:12:55.380 --> 01:13:00.155 align:middle line:84%
and obliterating our immediate
personalized space-time locus,

01:13:00.155 --> 01:13:04.154 align:middle line:84%
and falling into the
imagination, which

01:13:04.154 --> 01:13:10.100 align:middle line:84%
is running like a river
through all of us endlessly,

01:13:10.100 --> 01:13:19.970 align:middle line:84%
driven by the hydraulic moment
of the cataracts of chaos,

01:13:19.970 --> 01:13:23.942 align:middle line:84%
which usher into the
creativity of the imagination.

01:13:23.942 --> 01:13:28.379 align:middle line:84%
I mean, these river
metaphors are just endlessly

01:13:28.379 --> 01:13:32.700 align:middle line:84%
applicable to this-- the flowing
of forces over landscapes,

01:13:32.700 --> 01:13:35.802 align:middle line:84%
the pressure of chaos
on the imagination

01:13:35.802 --> 01:13:38.478 align:middle line:90%
to create creativity.

01:13:38.478 --> 01:13:42.910 align:middle line:84%
And it's looping
back into the same.

01:13:42.910 --> 01:13:50.950 align:middle line:84%
And these things are the icons
for the world that wants to be.

01:13:50.950 --> 01:13:56.280 align:middle line:84%
But the key is surrender
dissolution of boundaries,

01:13:56.280 --> 01:14:00.640 align:middle line:84%
dissolution of the
ego, and a trust

01:14:00.640 --> 01:14:05.510 align:middle line:84%
in the love of the
goddess, which transcends

01:14:05.510 --> 01:14:07.240 align:middle line:90%
rational understanding.

01:14:07.240 --> 01:14:08.800 align:middle line:84%
There will come a
moment, which will

01:14:08.800 --> 01:14:11.794 align:middle line:90%
be an absolute leap into space.

01:14:11.794 --> 01:14:15.055 align:middle line:84%
And we will simply have to
have the faith that there

01:14:15.055 --> 01:14:19.350 align:middle line:84%
is something waiting there,
because the dominator style has

01:14:19.350 --> 01:14:22.390 align:middle line:90%
left us no choice.

01:14:22.390 --> 01:15:41.226 align:middle line:90%